		{"id": "title", "type": "text", "x": -1400, "y": -1080, "width": 2320, "height": 140, "color": "6", "text": "# KTG Publish Pipeline\nGood AI / KTG content vault `_content` — .raw clip → ingest → draft → MEDIUM-READY → posted. State as of 2026-07-17: 12 articles catalogued, 2 medium-ready, 1 ready-full, **posted/ empty**."},
		{"id": "flow-mermaid", "type": "text", "x": -1360, "y": -600, "width": 840, "height": 460, "text": "```mermaid\nflowchart TD\n    RAW[\".raw/ source clips (immutable)\"] --> ING[\"ingest → wiki/sources + index\"]\n    ING --> DR[\"drafts/ — 12 catalogued, 6 series pieces still draft\"]\n    DR --> GATE{\"review gate: packaging + fact-check\"}\n    GATE -->|pass| MR[\"MEDIUM-READY-* — 2 packaged, 1 ready-full\"]\n    GATE -->|rework| DR\n    MR --> POST[\"posted/ — EMPTY, nothing live yet\"]\n```"},
		{"id": "flow-note", "type": "text", "x": -1360, "y": -100, "width": 840, "height": 160, "text": "**Pipeline reality check:** packaging is running ahead of drafting — two `medium-ready` pieces exist while several source drafts are still rough. Root files are mirrored under `drafts/` (~Jul 13 timestamps); `posted/` is empty, so everything is pre-publish."},
