		{"id": "status-fab", "type": "text", "x": 320, "y": -600, "width": 560, "height": 180, "color": "4", "text": "**status: medium-ready**\n\"The Silicon Oracle Has a Broken Fuel Gauge\" — ~2400 words, 9–11 min. Packaging complete: A/B titles, tags, canonical URL to ktg.one. Repackages the 02/03 drafts."},
