		{"id": "status-sccd", "type": "text", "x": 320, "y": -380, "width": 560, "height": 180, "color": "4", "text": "**status: medium-ready**\n\"SCCD: A Decision Model That Stops the Lie Before It Ships\" — Part 2, 8–10 min. `depends_on:` Silicon Oracle, so it ships second. `sccd_tfab.py` implementation already working."},
