		{"id": "next-callout", "type": "text", "x": 0, "y": 280, "width": 880, "height": 480, "color": "1", "text": "> [!todo] Pick ONE and ship\n> **Strongest candidate: `MEDIUM-READY-Model-Handbook-2026-The-Fabrication-Frontier.md`**\n>\n> Why this one:\n> - Only piece with packaging 100% done — A/B titles, subtitle, tags, read-time, canonical URL\n> - `posted/` is empty; the whole series needs a live anchor\n> - SCCD Part 2 declares `depends_on` this piece — shipping it unblocks the next publish\n> - POST-2 is close behind but still owes 2 table→PNG exports\n>\n> **Do:** final read-through → publish to Medium + ktg.one → move file to `posted/` → log it in `wiki/log.md`."}
